  "title": "E-Commerce & Digital Marketing Executive (Regional)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Join Our Team! 🚀</strong><br>\nWe’re looking for a passionate <strong>E-Commerce &amp; Digital Marketing Executive (Regional) </strong>to help us grow our online presence and bring our home appliances to more customers across the region. If you’re skilled in online marketplaces, love data, and enjoy creating impactful campaigns — we want to hear from you!</p>\n<p><strong>Your Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead our online store operations across platforms like Shopee, Lazada, TikTok, and more.</li>\n  <li>Drive exciting regional campaigns, from mega sale events to new product launches.</li>\n  <li>Analyse sales performance, track KPIs, and develop data-driven strategies.</li>\n  <li>Work with regional and local teams to optimise visibility and ensure smooth execution.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>You Should Have:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A degree in Marketing, Business, or E-Commerce.</li>\n  <li>3–5 years of experience in online sales or marketplace management.</li>\n  <li>A results-oriented mindset and proven success in driving e-commerce growth.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
